Write test: TrainingConfig accepts max_epochs=0 for zero-shot. File: tests/v2/unit/config/test_training_config_zero_shot.py
```python def test_training_config_allows_zero_epochs(): """max_epochs=0 must be valid for zero-shot evaluation (Glitch #12).""" from minivess.config.models import TrainingConfig config = TrainingConfig(max_epochs=0) assert config.max_epochs == 0
def test_training_config_rejects_negative_epochs(): """max_epochs must be >= 0.""" from minivess.config.models import TrainingConfig with pytest.raises(ValidationError): TrainingConfig(max_epochs=-1) ``` Expected: FAILS (current ge=1 rejects 0)
